The live stations at Pergola where you can choose from the catch of the day, buffet breakfast with the typical Malabar delicacies at Keraleeyam, the lip-smacking spread at Mavoor cafe, the little islands of seating created, the vertical garden, Raviz Calicut is a perfect get-away dining place for the foodie in you.
